review_blob: Wow. This is FANTASTIC! I was expecting a total in your face hop bomb, bit didnt get it. This is an awesome high octane IPA with great balance for a super hopped beer.

Justin on the Sunday Session always raves about this. I?ve had lots of Heretic before but this is my first Evil Twin. It is hoppy for a red ale, but is VERY well balanced. I see myself seeking this out in the future.
Got a 1/2bbl of this from the brewery for the kegerator in my office. This is a great daily drinker at 5.0% ABV and is a style that appeals to a large number of peoples palates.
